    ('SLAV-C 366', 'CZECH CINEMA', '30223', 'Class Status', 'TuTh Tuesday, Thursday 3:55 PM–5:10 PM', 'GA 0011', 'Craig Cravens', 4, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'GLOBAL & INTERNATIONAL STUDIES', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Introduces important trends and movements within the history of Czech cinematography. Places the films in their historical, cultural, and political contexts and illustrates how Czech films captured the life of Czech society during different periods. Examines the region of the Czech Republic/Czechoslovakia and Central Europe: its history, geography, ethnography and languages.', ARRAY['COLL (CASE) A&H Breadth of Inquiry credit
COLL (CASE) Culture Studies: Global Civ & Culture'], NULL),
